ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Tsuu T'ina Nation Reserve No. 145, Alberta
PrecisOrder setting apart approximately 1.214 hectares (3 acres) of land for the use and benefit of the TSUU T'INA NATION as an addition to TSUU T'INA NATION RESERVE NO. 145, located within the boundaries of the First Nation's existing reserve, just outside Calgary, Alberta.
